heading: Raethwind Wilds Dungeon Guide
content: Raethwind Wilds slow dungeon with a mediocre Codex entry, the . Overall, this isn't too bad for a first completion, but beyond gathering Renown and the aspect, it's better to focus on other dungeons instead for XP and Nightmare Sigils. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
